<inglise> COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 583/1999 of 17 March 1999 on the maximum amount of the Community's financial contribution to be paid to the Member States concerned in accordance with Council Regulation (EC) No 723/97 </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (E&Uuml;) nr 583/1999 asjaomastele liikmesriikidele vastavalt n&otilde;ukogu m&auml;&auml;rusele (E&Uuml;) nr 723/97 makstava &uuml;henduse rahalise toetuse &uuml;lemm&auml;&auml;ra kohta 17. m&auml;rts 1999 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa &Uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EC) No 723/97 of 22 April 1997 on the implementation of Member States' action programmes on control of EAGGF Guarantee Section expenditure (1), and in particular Article 4(2) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 22. aprilli 1997. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (E&Uuml;) nr 723/97 liikmesriikide tegevusprogrammide rakendamise kohta Euroopa P&otilde;llumajanduse Arendus- ja Tagatisfondi tagatisrahastu kulude kontrollimisel, (1) eriti selle artikli 4 l&otilde;iget 2, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the Fund Committee has been consulted; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: fondikomiteega on konsulteeritud; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 1 of Regulation (EC) No 723/97 provides that the Community shall contribute towards the costs incurred by Member States in implementing new action programmes, arising out of new Community obligations; whereas Article 4(2) of the same Regulation provides that the Commission shall, after consulting the Fund Committee, set the maximum annual amount of the Community's financial contribution having regard to the appropriations and on the basis of the information supplied by the Member States concerned; whereas the amount in question shall be granted in accordance with Article 3 of Commission Regulation (EC) No 1780/97 (2), laying down the rules of application of Regulation (EC) No 723/97, as last amended by the Regulation (EC) No 1890/98 (3); that the Member States concerned have supplied the relevant information to the Commission for the year 1999, </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 723/97 artiklis 1 s&auml;testatakse, et &uuml;hendus rahastab liikmesriikide kulusid, mis tekivad seoses uutest &uuml;henduse kohustustest tulenevate uute tegevusprogrammide rakendamisega; k&otilde;nealuse m&auml;&auml;ruse artikli 4 l&otilde;ikes 2 s&auml;testatakse, et komisjon m&auml;&auml;rab p&auml;rast fondikomiteega konsulteerimist eraldisi arvesse v&otilde;ttes ja asjaomaste liikmesriikide poolt esitatud teabe p&otilde;hjal kindlaks &uuml;henduse rahalise toetuse &uuml;lemm&auml;&auml;ra; k&otilde;nealune summa antakse vastavalt komisjoni m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 1780/97 (milles s&auml;testatakse m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 723/97 rakenduseeskirjad, (2) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1890/98 (3)) artiklile 3; asjaomased liikmesriigid on esitanud komisjonile 1999. aasta kohta asjakohase teabe; </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> The maximum amount of the Community's financial contribution towards the costs incurred by the Member States concerned in implementing action programmes on control of EAGGF Guarantee Section expenditure for 1999, provided for by Council Regulation (EC) No 723/97 is set out in the Annex of this Regulation. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse lisas on esitatud &uuml;henduse rahalise toetuse &uuml;lemm&auml;&auml;r, mis makstakse liikmesriikidele m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 723/97 etten&auml;htud Euroopa P&otilde;llumajanduse Arendus- ja Tagatisfondi tagatisrahastu 1999. aasta kulude kontrollimisega seotud tegevusprogrammide rakendamisel tekkivate kulude rahastamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the seventh day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub seitsmendal p&auml;eval p&auml;rast selle avaldamist Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 17 March 1999. </inglise>
<eesti> Br&uuml;ssel, 17. m&auml;rts 1999 </eesti>
